page_title: Azure OpenAI Service Assistants Python & REST API runs reference
page_description: Learn how to use Azure OpenAI's Python & REST API runs with Assistants.
chunk_content: Message delta objectRepresents a message delta. For example any changed fields on a message during streaming.|Name | Type | Description ||---  |---   |---         || `id` | string | The identifier of the message, which can be referenced in API endpoints. || `object` | string | The object type, which is always `thread.message.delta`. || `delta` | object | The delta containing the fields that have changed on the Message. |
